OL,3,CNew EU entry system in force: How does
OL,4,Cit work and could you be delayed?
OL,6,FPassengers without EU passports will
OL,7,Fbe required to have their fingerprints
OL,8,Fand photographs taken, as Consumer
OL,9,FCorrespondent Chris Choi reports
OL,11,FMany UK passengers are suffering
OL,12,Fdelays at airports in continental
OL,13,FEurope because of the rollout of a new
OL,14,FEntry/Exit system.
OL,16,FPhysical stamps from passport officers
OL,17,Fare being phased out in place of a
OL,18,Fdigital biometric system, in a bid to
OL,19,Fmake entering the EU from non-Schengen
OL,20,Farea countries quicker.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
