OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777489866
OL,3,CNew EU entry system in force: How does
OL,4,Cit work and could you be delayed?
OL,6,FIt has been introduced to strengthen
OL,7,Fborder security, detect overstays and
OL,8,Fis supposed to improve processing
OL,9,Fspeeds at airports.
OL,11,FHowever, concerns remain that the new
OL,12,Fsystem, which began its progressive
OL,13,Frollout in October 2025 and became
OL,14,Ffully operational on April 10, is
OL,15,Fcausing delays as airports continue to
OL,16,Fadjust to the new rules.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777489866
OL,3,CNew EU entry system in force: How does
OL,4,Cit work and could you be delayed?
OL,6,FUntil recently, many airports were
OL,7,Feffectively running a double system,
OL,8,Fwith both passport stamps being taken
OL,9,Fand the new biometric digital EES
OL,10,F(Entry/Exit system) also being carried
OL,11,Fout.
OL,13,FThis double-entry recording has led to
OL,14,Fnumerous delays at airports across the
OL,15,Fbloc, with Brits complaining of multi-
OL,16,Fhour waits to get through airports,
OL,17,Fand there are concerns that the
OL,18,Fchanges could cause further delays for
OL,19,Ftravellers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
