PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777489866
OL,3,CNew EU entry system in force: How does
OL,4,Cit work and could you be delayed?
OL,6,FITV News explains how the new system
OL,7,Fworks.
OL,9,FWhat is the Entry/Exit system?
OL,11,FNon-EU nationals wishing to enter the
OL,12,FSchengen area will now go through
OL,13,Fbiometric checks instead of getting a
OL,14,Fpassport stamp when entering the area.
OL,16,FThese checks will involve face scans
OL,17,Fand fingerprint recording. Children
OL,18,Funder the age of 12 will not need to
OL,19,Fhave their fingerprints scanned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
