OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777489866
OL,3,CNew EU entry system in force: How does
OL,4,Cit work and could you be delayed?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FTravellers will also go through the
OL,12,Fsame check when leaving the area,
OL,13,Fmeaning countries can track when
OL,14,Fvisitors overstay.
OL,16,FOnce registered, subsequent entries to
OL,17,Fthe bloc will be quicker, as the
OL,18,Fbiometrics will only need to be
OL,19,Fscanned rather than registered. The
OL,20,Fdigital record will be valid for three
OL,21,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
