OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777489866
OL,3,CNew EU entry system in force: How does
OL,4,Cit work and could you be delayed?
OL,6,FIt should only take a few minutes, but
OL,7,Fthere have been reports of significant
OL,8,Fdelays as airports struggle with the
OL,9,Fnew system.
OL,11,FThere is a small list of other
OL,12,Fexceptions for UK nationals, which can
OL,13,Fbe found on the EES website.
OL,15,FWhy has the EU introduced the new
OL,16,Fsystem?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
